Package ie.gmit.ngrams.builders

Build the ngrams objects

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatabaseBuilder
    Define methods to build the database.
    DatabaseBuildPlan
    Set the plan for build the database, contains the main parts: the map and the distance calculator.
    KmerGeneratorFactoryInterface
    Define a factory for create
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatabaseBuildManager
    Build different types of databases based on the DatabaseBuilder, implemented as a Eagle singleton.
    KmerGeneratorFactory
    Factory for KmerGenerator.
    LongKmer3EncodeDatabaseBuilder
    Build a database with kmers of size 3 using long for store kmers in binary .
    LongKmer4EncodeDatabase
    Build a database with kmers of size four using long for store kmers in binary .
